      <title>金莺队在 ChiSox 拉力赛中幸存，以 8-6 赢得比赛，最终以内场飞球和干扰判罚结束</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/orioles-white-sox-score-a12ca8c2d11a9638826b4692fe5df90f</link>
